<plot>Spring training has ended and the baseball pennant chase, in the National League, is already under way in St. Louis, Chicago and Brooklyn. The use of slow-motion cameras gives shots of baseball plays not usually revealed at the regular 35 mm camera speed. 1940 baseball players seen close-up and in action include 'Dizzy" Dean, Carl Hubbell, "Arky" Vaughan, "Gabby" Hartnett, Joe Medwick, Merrill May and Ernie Lombardi.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?452643</url></doc>
